For Display:
- MainDisplay class to display the GUI
- There will be other smaller classes to display parts of the GUI:

For Background Work
- Manager class to receive trigger from GUI, execute functions of other classes and return result for the GUI to display  
- Box class to hold (color or order) values of boxes displayed in the GUI
- BoxCollection class ( queue or stack in array or linked list) to hold list of boxes
- Level class hold values to determine the difficulity of the games like speed, time, number of box
- Player class hold player's input name and their highest score
- PlayerCollection class to hold list of ones have played the games


